		"description": "<p>You are a true creature of the wilderness, fast, ferocious, and lethal. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Wisdom score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>Half your berserker levels count as ranger levels for the purpose of the @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.q1v63h8j4a87n3t0]{Extra Attack} and @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.n83irh1dygryy7q8]{Stride and Seek} features.</li>\n<li>Your speed increases by 5 feet.</li>\n<li>While you are raging, the bonus to attack from @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.yuncbhlz6js1w4t4]{Hunter's Target} increases to +2 and the bonus damage increases to 1d8.</li>\n</ul>",
